root: ^(I made it to the third house)
^(This one is a starter home with a nice family feel to it)
^(This location is the closest to David's work)
^(It also has a fantastic daycare nearby)
^(It is lacking in quite a few areas however)
^(There is no in-ground pool, only an above-ground one)
^(There is also no in-law suite or home theater)
^(There is a redeeming factor with this home though)
^(It is significantly less then their budget with a listing of $1.4M)
^(It needs a lot of work but with the leftover money in the budget)
^(I don't seem to have any more promising listings)
^(So, time to head back to David and Sarah and let them know what I found)
